Notes: Game #3 of the 2005 Pepsi Tip-Off hosted by Minnesota State University.

UWS's Molly Hendricks sets Pepsi-Tip Off single-game assist record (11).
Game.Officials: Anne Nehring,  Jon Garrow,  Mike Klinedinst
